snippet.title: Crab God - Release trailer
snippet.description:
Buy the game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2289390/Crab_God/?utm_source=Youtube&utm_campaign=releasetrailer

Crab God is an atmospheric underwater strategy game. Guide your Crabling colony through wild ocean depths, and defend the egg of the next Crab God. Restore and protect diverse coral reefs, making a difference in the real world as you progress in-game. Make waves, praise the claw!

Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2289390/Crab_God/
Official website - https://firesquid.games/games/crab-god
Newsletter - https://bit.ly/CrabGodNews
Twitter - https://twitter.com/crabgodgame
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/crabgodgame/
Discord - https://discord.gg/vsxD6n8P8J

Trailer maker: Friday Afternoons
Sound design: Valentin Frin
Developed by Chaos Theory Games
Published by Firesquid
